OL,5, The UK's first city mayor to declare a 
OL,6, climate crisis has been questioned for 
OL,7, flying nine hours to attend a          
OL,8, conference to urge leaders to cut CO2. 
OL,10,FBristol Mayor Marvin Rees told the TED 
OL,11,Fconference in Canada that city mayors  
OL,12,Fcould influence carbon policy.         
OL,14,FClimate campaigners Flight Free UK     
OL,15,Fcalculated the trip created 2.016      
OL,16,Ftonnes (2,016kg) of CO2 per passenger  
OL,17,Fand was at odds with his message.      
OL,19,FThe mayor's office said he had a full  
OL,20,Fagenda with networking opportunities.  
